## Errors
401= login, wrong password
403= not logged in

## Login
POST /login {password} -> if ok then cookie else HTTP 401
POST /logout {}
POST /set_password {password}
GET /login_mode {}
POST /login_mode {mode} // true, false

## Auto or Manual mode
GET /switching_mode {}
POST /switching_mode {mode} // on, off, auto_days, auto_temp
GET /auto_days_prog {}
POST /auto_days_prog {prog}
GET /auto_temp {}
POST /auto_temp {temp}

## Diagnostics
GET /temp {}
GET /version {}
POST /time {area}
GET /time {}
POST /identifier {string}
GET /identifier {}